<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>323</hymn_number>
<author>Bilby</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vory ny mpanomponao
 Eto anatrehanao,
 Ry Jesosy Tomponay !
 He ! faly ny fonay,
 Faly, faly, faly,
 He ! faly ny fonay,
 Vory maro toy izao.

[V2]
 Mba atrehonao iizahay
 Fa mitokana eto izao
 Ny trano ho Anao :
 He ! faly ..sns.

[V3]
 Eto hitorianay
 An'i Jeso Tomponay,
 Mpamonjy lehibe :
 He ! faly ..sns.

[V4]
 Eto hanomezanao
 Tsara ny Fanahinao
 Mba hanadio ny fo :
 He ! faly ..sns.

[V5]
 Eto no hanananao
 Laza saotra ho Anao ;
 Ny maro mba vonjeo :
 He ! faly ..sns.

[V6]
 Aoka re ny tranonay,
 Trano iangonanay,
 Mba ho tempolinao :
 He ! faly ..sns.</lyrics>
<title>Vory ny mpanomponay FFPM323</title>
</song>